::I, too, am a Texan.  It's Boo-ee knife, Boo-ee High, Boo-ee County, etc. [[User:Tuckerresearch|TuckerResearch]] ([[User talk:Tuckerresearch|talk]]) 22:48, 5 July 2016 (UTC)
